snippet.title: The Amazing Maze (Midway, 1976) Arcade Video Game
snippet.description:
Rare video arcade game manufactured by Midway in 1976.  An early maze video game, but not the first (Gotcha 1973 Atari).  Kinda fun two player.  Unfortunately sound was a manufacturer add-on option and not standard.  

More info: http://www.arcade-history.com/?n=amazing-maze&page=detail&id=75
